'''李·大衛·保耶'''（{{lang-en|'''Lee David Bowyer'''}}，{{bd|1977年|1月3日|catIdx=Bowyer, Lee}}）出生在[[景寧鎮|景寧鎮]]，是一名[[英格蘭|英格蘭]][[職業|職業]][[足球|足球]][[運動員|運動員]]，司職[[中場|中場]]，現時是自由身球員，他曾代表[[英格蘭足球代表隊|英格蘭]]上陣過1場。

保耶是直至[[2010年至2011年英格蘭超級聯賽|2010/11年球季]]在[[英超|英超]]累計領取[[黃牌|黃牌]]最多的球員，合共101面黃牌比[[奇雲·戴維斯|奇雲·戴維斯]]、[[羅比·沙維治|羅比·沙維治]]及[[保羅·史高斯|保羅·史高斯]]等硬漢還要多，他同時亦有5面[[紅牌|紅牌]]記錄。

== 生平 ==
=== 球會 ===
===查爾頓===
1994年，保耶成為[[查爾頓競技|查爾頓]]的一員<ref name=sbase1>[http://www.soccerbase.com/players_details.sd?playerid=870 Soccerbase: Lee Bowyer] {{WebCite|url=https://www.webcitation.org/692Y8bLsr?url=http://www.soccerbase.com/players/player.sd?player_id=870 |date=20120710002721 |dateformat=iso }}, Racing Post. 參閱於2007年6月19日</ref>。1994年，他和其同伴{{Link-en|甸恩·錢德勒|Dean Chandler}}因為雙雙吸食[[大麻|大麻]]而受到注意<ref>{{cite news
|date=2006-12-13
|url=http://sport.guardian.co.uk/news/story/0,,1970796,00.html
|title=Caborn attacked on plan to ease dope rules
|publisher=[[衛報|衛報]]
|accessdate=2006-12-30
|archive-date=2007-11-28
|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071128091324/http://sport.guardian.co.uk/news/story/0,,1970796,00.html
|dead-url=no
}}</ref>，他們亦因此被長期禁賽，但是保耶卻得已重返一隊效力，並為查爾頓上陣了58場並攻入14球<ref name=sbase1 />。

=== 列斯聯 ===
1996年，當時的[[列斯聯足球會|列斯聯]]領隊[[侯活·韋健遜|韋健遜]]以280萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]簽入了保耶，不久後，他被控涉嫌種族歧視<ref>{{cite news
|date=2003-01-13|url=http://www.mirror.co.uk/news/columnists/parsons/2003/01/13/bowyer-s-a-soccer-player--not-a-saint-89520-12526541/|title= Bowyer's a soccer player, not a saint|publisher=The Daily Mirror|accessdate=2006-12-30}}</ref>。1999–00球季，他是當時領隊{{Link-en|大衛·奧拉利|David O'Leary}}手下的重要球員，並協助列斯聯闖進[[欧洲联盟杯|欧洲联盟杯]]四強，另外在2000-01又打進了冠軍聯賽。他曾經在1998–99和2000–01兩個球季當選為列斯聯年度最佳球員。
2003年1月，保耶轉投[[韋斯咸足球會|韋斯咸]]<ref name=whu>{{cite news|date=2003-02-11|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/w/west_ham_utd/2631615.stm|title=Bowyer signs for Hammers|publisher=BBC News|accessdate=2007-01-19|archive-date=2003-12-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20031216084408/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/w/west_ham_utd/2631615.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>，他一共代表列斯聯上陣257場並攻入62球<ref name=sbase1 />。

=== 韋斯咸 ===
保耶與韋斯咸簽下六個月的合約，不幸的是韋斯咸在2002–03球季降班<ref>{{cite news|date=2003-01-07|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/2634745.stm|title=Bowyer transfer-listed|publisher=BBC News|accessdate=2007-01-23|archive-date=2003-12-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20031217071055/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/2634745.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他因傷患困擾，僅上陣了11場<ref name=whufc1>{{cite news|date=2003-05-16|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/w/west_ham_utd/3034593.stm|title=Hammers release Bowyer|publisher=BBC News|accessdate=2007-06-23|archive-date=2003-06-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20030607040942/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/w/west_ham_utd/3034593.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>，後來他被球會放棄<ref name=whufc1 />。

=== 紐卡素 ===
2002–03球季，韋斯咸降班後，保耶隨即在2003年7月轉會至[[紐卡素足球會|紐卡素]]<ref>{{cite news|date=2003-07-01|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/n/newcastle_united/3031656.stm|title=Bowyer makes Magpies move|publisher=BBC News|accessdate=2007-06-19|archive-date=2004-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20040610005601/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/n/newcastle_united/3031656.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。 

2005年4月，保耶在對[[阿士東維拉足球會|阿士東維拉]]的賽事中與隊友[[基隆·代尔|代尔]]打架，兩人均領紅離場，並再賽後加罰停賽三場，紐卡素會方亦向他索取其六星期的總工資作為罰款<ref name="multiple">{{cite news|date=2006-07-05 |url=http://www.cnn.com/2006/SPORT/football/07/05/england.bowyer/index.html|title= Court fine Bowyer over Dyer fight|publisher=[[CNN|CNN]]|accessdate=2006-12-30}}</ref>。保耶總共代表紐卡素上陣98場射入11球<ref name=sbase1 />。

=== 韋斯咸 ===
2006年6月，保耶重返他年少時支持的韋斯咸<ref>{{cite news|date=2006-06-18|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/w/west_ham_utd/5062362.stm|title=West Ham sign midfielder Bowyer|publisher=BBC News|accessdate=2007-06-19|archive-date=2018-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180511222250/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/w/west_ham_utd/5062362.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2007年1月，他在對[[雷丁足球會|雷丁]]的賽事中弄傷[[肩膀|肩膀]]，導致在2006/07球季，他僅上陣了22場<ref>{{cite news|date=2006-01-02|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/w/west_ham_utd/6224347.stm|title=Bowyer injury blow for West Ham|publisher=BBC News|accessdate=2007-07-01|archive-date=2007-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070120062724/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/w/west_ham_utd/6224347.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。然而，他很快痊癒了。2007/08年球季，保耶成功爭取了在韋斯咸的正選地位，在對[[韋根體育足球會|韋根]]的賽事中攻入效力的首球。

2009年1月9日，保耶被外借到[[英格蘭足球冠軍聯賽|英冠]]球隊[[伯明翰城足球俱乐部|伯明翰城]]直到季末<ref>{{cite news |language=en |date=2009-01-09 |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/birmingham_city/7819728.stm |title=Birmingham snap up Bowyer on loan |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |accessdate=2009-01-09 |archive-date=2019-03-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190322140111/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/birmingham_city/7819728.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，期間上陣17場，射入1球及領得1面[[紅牌|紅牌]]，協助球隊奪得聯賽亞軍及直接升級[[英格蘭足球超級聯賽|英超]]席位。

=== 伯明翰城 ===
2009年7月9日於保耶與韋斯咸的合約屆滿後，他正式轉投[[伯明翰足球會|伯明翰城]]，簽約兩年<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/birmingham_city/8140142.stm |title=Birmingham seal deal for Bowyer |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2009-07-09 |accessdate=2011-07-11 |archive-date=2018-07-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180702023756/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/birmingham_city/8140142.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。保耶表現持續出色，在對[[富勒姆足球俱乐部|富咸]]與[[伍尔弗汉普顿流浪足球俱乐部|狼隊]]連續兩場[[英超|英超]]射入奠勝球<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/8364358.stm |title=Birmingham 1-0 Fulham |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2009-11-21 |accessdate=2011-07-11 |archive-date=2018-07-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180702035943/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/8364358.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/8377163.stm |title=Wolverhampton   0 - 1   Birmingham |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2009-11-29 |accessdate=2011-07-11 |archive-date=2018-07-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180702013217/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/8377163.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。期間協助球隊連續在各項賽事15場保持不敗，並創下球會在頂級聯賽連續12場不敗記錄，以第9位結束球季，是伯明翰城超過50年來最佳成績。

2010年11月20日保耶於[[格力·加特拿|格力·加特拿]]因傷缺陣而獲派上陣主場出戰[[切尔西足球俱乐部|車路士]]，射入賽事唯一入球擊敗領頭羊兼帶領球隊脫離降班區域<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/9192022.stm |title=Birmingham 1-0 Chelsea |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2010-11-20 |accessdate=2011-07-11 |archive-date=2021-01-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210120112553/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/9192022.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>；他其後於主場對[[曼徹斯特聯足球俱樂部|曼聯]]在完場前射入為主隊扳平1-1<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/9312846.stm |title=Birmingham 1-1 Man Utd |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2010-12-28 |accessdate=2011-07-11 |archive-date=2017-08-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170831103307/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/9312846.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2011年[[元旦|元旦]]主場0-3負於[[阿森纳足球俱乐部|阿仙奴]]，保耶故意踏中[[巴卡雷·薩尼亞|薩尼亞]]，雖然當場球證{{le|彼得·禾頓|Peter Walton (referee)|禾頓}}沒有看到事發經過，但電視重播清楚拍下罪證<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/teams/birmingham-city/8238289/Birmingham-manager-Alex-McLeish-accuses-FA-of-picking-on-smaller-club.html |title=Birmingham manager Alex McLeish accuses FA of picking on smaller club |publisher=''telegraph.co.uk'' |date=2011-01-04 |accessdate=2011-07-11 |archive-date=2019-04-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190402114204/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/teams/birmingham-city/8238289/Birmingham-manager-Alex-McLeish-accuses-FA-of-picking-on-smaller-club.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，因而被判罰停賽3場<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/birmingham_city/9337014.stm |title=Birmingham's Lee Bowyer receives three-match ban |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-01-04 |accessdate=2011-07-11 |archive-date=2018-07-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180705205733/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/birmingham_city/9337014.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2011年2月27日伯明翰城在[[溫布萊球場|溫布萊球場]]於[[2011年英格蘭聯賽盃決賽|聯賽盃決賽]]迎戰[[阿森纳足球俱乐部|阿仙奴]]，正選上陣的保耶協助球隊成功爆冷門以2-1獲勝，取得個人首面重要錦標獎牌<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/league_cup/9405702.stm |title=Arsenal 1-2 Birmingham |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-02-27 |accessdate=2011-07-11 |archive-date=2020-01-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200108182845/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/league_cup/9405702.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

雖然領隊[[亚历克斯·麥克萊什|麥克萊什]]向保耶表示來季會與他續約一年<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/13394033.stm |title=Lee Bowyer to be offered new Birmingham contract |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-05-13 |accessdate=2011-07-11 |archive-date=2011-05-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110516155923/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/13394033.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但球隊卻於球季結束後降班[[英冠|英冠]]，保耶於約滿後離隊<ref>{{cite news|language=en |url=http://www.bcfc.com/page/News/NewsDetail/0,,10412~2367559,00.html |title=CARR GEARS UP |publisher=[[伯明翰足球會|''bcfc.com'']] |date=2011-05-27 |accessdate=2011-07-11 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110530173025/http://www.bcfc.com/page/News/NewsDetail/0%2C%2C10412~2367559%2C00.html |archivedate=2011-05-30 }}</ref>。

=== 葉士域治 ===
2011年7月10日[[英冠|英冠]]球會[[伊普斯维奇城足球俱乐部|葉士域治]]成功免費羅致保耶，簽約一年<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/14101570.stm |title=Midfielder Lee Bowyer joins Ipswich Town |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-07-10 |accessdate=2011-07-11 |archive-date=2011-07-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110716013336/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/14101570.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 國家隊 ==
保耶效力列斯聯期間一直是[[英格蘭21歲以下足球代表隊|英格蘭U21]]的成員<ref>{{cite news|date=|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/shared/bsp/hi/football/statistics/players/b/bowyer_17305.stm|title=Squad Profiles: Lee Bowyer|publisher=BBC Sport|accessdate=2007-06-23|archive-date=2007-03-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070315152500/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/shared/bsp/hi/football/statistics/players/b/bowyer_17305.stm|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。
 
2002年9月，當時英軍領隊[[斯文·約蘭·艾歷臣|艾歷臣]]挑選了他出戰對[[葡萄牙國家足球隊|葡萄牙]]的友賽<ref>{{cite news|date=2002-09-02|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/2231000.stm|title=Leeds duo in England squad|publisher=BBC Sport|accessdate=2007-06-19|archive-date=2004-05-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20040510043649/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/2231000.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他在該場賽事首次上陣，並交予助攻給[[阿倫·史密夫|阿倫·史密夫]]<ref>{{cite news |date=2002-09-07 |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/internationals/england/2242638.stm |title=Portugal hold England |publisher=BBC Sport |accessdate=2007-06-19 |archive-date=2004-06-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20040627193520/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/internationals/england/2242638.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。這也是保耶唯一一次代表英軍上陣。

